highlights.text: “Lapada Dela - Ao Vivo” by Grupo Menos É Mais and Matheus Fernandes has been on Top Songs Brazil the longest, at 878 days straight.
Henrique & Juliano has the most spots on Top Songs Brazil. “Última Saudade - Ao Vivo” is the highest at #10.
“Toque de Mágica - Ao Vivo” by Traia Véia is the highest new entry on Top Songs Brazil at #195.
“Don’t Say You Love Me” by Jin is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Brazil, up 123 spots at #63.
